<refnamediv id='name'>
<refname>isibus</refname>
<refpurpose>show sizes of backups</refpurpose>
</refnamediv>

<refsynopsisdiv id='synopsis'>
<cmdsynopsis>
  <command>isibus</command>
  <arg choice='opt'>--verbose</arg>
  <arg choice='opt'>--delay <replaceable>delay</replaceable></arg>
</cmdsynopsis>
</refsynopsisdiv>

<refsect1 id='description'><title>Description</title>
<para>
<application>ISiBackup</application> makes backup easy.
</para>
<para>
<command>isibus</command> shows the size of backups created by isibackup and stored locally at /var/backups/isibackup.
It creates an unsorted list and a list reversly sorted by size, which are both displayed on stdout.
</para>
</refsect1>

